Interface Expression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Expression.DateFormat, Expression.DayComputer, Expression.HourComputer, Expression.MinuteComputer, Expression.MonthComputer, Expression.SecondComputer, Expression.Substring, Expression.TruncateComputer, Expression.YearComputer

    public interface Expression
extends Serializable
    Produce a computation result for computed column.
